asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: B Rabbit
description: B-Rabbit has been given the opportunity to take everything he ever wanted. But he gets very nervous. He sweats easily in his palms and has weak knees. He loves spaghetti, but not his mums. Hers makes him sick. When he's nervous it is very hard to tell, he always looks calm. He often forgets things, even if he wrote it down, and occasionally mumbles his words. People laugh at him because of that. Times up? Not yet. When he snaps himself back he gets it right. Because he knows if he doesn't, he will have to back to the lab in the mobile home where he learns rap. So he makes sure he doesn't pass up opportunities. He has soul that is trying to escape his ****. But he knows he'll be king of the new world, where he'll be a superstar. He's getting older, and grumpier. Sometimes he gets angry and lashes out. But women love him. They hang on to him as he travels the world. But while he travels he gets further away from his family, when he comes home they barely recognise each other. Have a drink of water. Women don't like him as much anymore, he's gone cold. They've moved on because he fell over on a tv show. As it was told, so it unfolds friend. He's not playing games, he will alter the meaning of anger. Destroy a roof as two dogs in a cage could. He was once playing a game, but he's not in the mood anymore. Someone ate him. But he kept singing because he expects to be paid. With a lot of internal pain already, being poor added to it. He worked 9 to 5 and buys food with stamps. This isn't a movie, this is B-Rabbits life. Time are hard for him and they appear to be getting harder. He sometimes tries to grow plants from a seed while playing on the teeter totter. It is hard for him to both a Father and a leading female Opera singer. The baby who's a mother keeps screaming at him so much he wants to move a lot. When the days feel the same he slows down. So he needs to make a good plan or he'll end up somewhere he doesn't want to be. He can only succeed, there is no option to fail now. He loves his mum, but not her mobile home and spaghetti. He doesn't want to retire in Salem. So he's having shots and hopes not to trip over while he "loses himself" in the music he's listening to.

name: Charlotte de Bunny
description:
Thought to be fiction written by Harewood Lloyd, Charlotte de Bunny is indeed a Pirate Captian most notorious. 

Falling in love with a humble sailor, and dressing as a man to follow him, Charlotte de Bunny was kept in a cage by the ship’s captain and used for shampoo irritation experiments. 

By gaining the trust of the ship’s crew, Charlotte enacted a mutiny and became captain of the ship, renaming it ‘Queen Fluf’s Revenge’. Tragically, her first love sailor was drowned in the battle. 

Charlotte de Bunny at the helm of Queen Fluf’s Revenge terrorised and raised Fat Boomer Pig merchant ships, until she was run aground in Africa. Retreating deep within the jungle, the crew survived for months off Jungle Carrots. 

A passing Dutch Mouse Cheese Flotilla in search of exotic rennets rescued the motley bunny and her crew, in exchange for the recipe for sensitive shampoo. 

Returning to this Brave New World with a taste for cheese and silky hair, Charlotte de Bunny searches for new hearts to win, and new adventures to explore!

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
